Class IValue

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryOperation, ExternalType, Literal, Operator, Priority, Return, UnaryOperation

    public class IValue
extends Value
    Node extension that represents something that returns a value. For the rules on what can and cannot be an value node, refer to Value.setType(java.lang.String)
